title: Conti Discovery Commands
id: 384d2e63-ff68-43d9-a332-0d3f80d12e58
status: experimental
description: Detects discovery commands commonly associated with Conti Ransomware.
id: 384d2e63-ff68-43d9-a332-0d3f80d12e58
references:
    - https://support.scythe.io/knowledge/conti-ransomware
    - https://thedfirreport.com/2021/05/12/conti-ransomware/
author: Tyler Casey @1qazCasey, @scythe_io
date: 2024/02/09
tags:
    - attack.discovery
    - attack.t1016
    - attack.t1082
    - attack.t1016
logsource:
    product: windows
    category: process_creation
detection:
    selection:
        CommandLine|contains:
            - 'ipconfig /all'
            - 'systeminfo'
            - 'whoami'
            - 'net'
    condition: selection
falsepositives:
    - Administrators may utilize these commands as part of system administration.  
level: low
